name: Femboy Clicker
description:
Femboy Clicker is a small, indie game produced by one developer - me. I was bored one friday and decided to make this hell-hole of a game, which I'm personally not proud of but hey, it is what it is.

It's not fully produced as of yet, however production is smooth and everything as off now functions.

There is a free promotional logo for download (so that I can appear on search)
